<pb ed="T" id="T19.0983A.0439c" n="0439c"/>
<lb n="0439c01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0439c02"/>
<lb n="0439c03"/><head type="no">No. 983A [cf. Nos. 982, 984, 985]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0439c04"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0439018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】仁和寺藏古寫本，【乙】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本，此軌宋元二本缺，〔佛說〕－【明】【乙】</note><app n="0439018"><lem>佛<note n="0439019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">說＝母【聖】【甲】＊</note><app n="0439019"><lem>說</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">母</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0439018" place="foot" type="rest">【原】麗本，【甲】仁和寺藏古寫本，【乙】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本，此軌宋元二本缺</note>大孔雀明王畫像壇場儀
<lb n="0439c05"/><note n="0439020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">軌＋（法）【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0439020"><lem>軌</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">軌法</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0439c06"/>
<lb n="0439c07"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0439021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（開府…寺）三十七字＝（唐北天竺）四字【明】【乙】，（特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺）十字【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0439021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（開府…寺）三十七字＝（唐北天竺）四字【明】【乙】，＝（特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺）十字【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0439021" word-count="37"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿
<lb n="0439c08"/>肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司
<lb n="0439c09"/>空諡大鑒正號大廣智大興善
<lb n="0439c10"/>寺</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">唐北天竺</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺</rdg></app>三藏沙<note n="0439022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">門＋（大廣智）【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0439022"><lem>門</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">門大廣智</rdg></app>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0439c11"/><p>佛告阿難陀。若諸世間所有災禍逼惱。刀兵
<lb n="0439c12"/>飢饉亢旱疾疫。四百四病憂<note n="0439023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惱＝苦【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0439023"><lem>惱</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">苦</rdg></app>&CB00508;諍。及八萬
<lb n="0439c13"/>四千鬼魅嬈惱有情。所求世間出世間勝願
<lb n="0439c14"/>多有障礙者。<note n="0439024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皆＝背【聖】</note><app n="0439024"><lem>皆</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">背</rdg></app>由無始已來貪愛無明。虛妄
<lb n="0439c15"/>分別三毒煩惱。不了實相積集不善。<note n="0439025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">感招＝敢&CB01456;【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0439025"><lem>感招</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">敢&CB01456;</rdg></app>如
<lb n="0439c16"/>是種種災難</p>
<lb n="0439c17"/><p>阿難陀是故我今為彼讀誦佛母大孔雀明王
<lb n="0439c18"/><note n="0439026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＝終【聖】</note><app n="0439026"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">終</rdg></app>者。<note n="0439027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔及一切災厄眾生〕－【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0439027"><lem>及一切災厄眾生</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。復說畫像法及建
<lb n="0439c19"/>立道場供養儀軌。若依此法轉讀是經。一切
<lb n="0439c20"/>災難皆得消除。所有願求隨意滿足。阿難陀
<lb n="0439c21"/>若有苦惱災難起時。或彼國王及諸王子大
<lb n="0439c22"/>臣妃后。及苾芻苾芻尼善男子善女人等。為
<lb n="0439c23"/>除災故。或於王宮或於勝地。或於清淨伽藍
<lb n="0439c24"/>或隨本所居宅舍。依法淨地掘深一肘。除去
<lb n="0439c25"/>瓦礫地中穢物。填滿淨土築令平正。其土本
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0983A.0440a" n="0440a"/>
<lb n="0440a01"/>淨&CB00230;用填之。若土有餘其地殊勝。應<note n="0440001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">泥拭＝&CB00410;穢【聖】，&CB00410;拭【甲】</note><note n="0440001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">泥拭＝&CB00410;穢【聖】，＝&CB00410;拭【甲】</note><app n="0440001"><lem>泥拭</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&CB00410;穢</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00410;拭</rdg></app>清
<lb n="0440a02"/>淨建立道場作五肘方壇。高四指量三重布
<lb n="0440a03"/>位。或以彩畫或用五色粉成。於內院中<note n="0440002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔心〕－【明】</note><app n="0440002"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0440a04"/>畫八葉蓮華。於蓮華<note n="0440003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔胎〕－【明】</note><app n="0440003"><lem>胎</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>上畫佛母大孔雀明
<lb n="0440a05"/>王菩薩。頭向東方白色。著白<note n="0440004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">繒＝增【聖】</note><app n="0440004"><lem>繒</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">增</rdg></app>輕衣。頭冠
<lb n="0440a06"/><note n="0440005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">瓔珞＝纓絡【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440005"><lem>瓔珞</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">纓絡</rdg></app>耳<note n="0440006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">璫＝蟷【聖】</note><app n="0440006"><lem>璫</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">蟷</rdg></app>臂釧種種莊嚴。乘金色孔雀<note n="0440007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔王〕－【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440007"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0440a07"/>結跏趺坐白蓮華上。<note n="0440008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔或青綠花上〕－【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440008"><lem>或青<note n="0440009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">綠＝蓮【明】【乙】</note><app n="0440009"><lem>綠</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">蓮</rdg></app>花上</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。住慈悲
<lb n="0440a08"/>相有四臂。右邊第一手執開敷蓮華。第二手
<lb n="0440a09"/>持俱緣果<note place="inline">其果狀<note n="0440010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔相〕－【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0440010"><lem>相</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>似水&CB00025;</note>左邊第一手當心掌持吉
<lb n="0440a10"/>祥&CB00031;<note n="0440011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔如桃李形〕－【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440011"><lem><note place="inline">如桃<note n="0440012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">李＝子&M062485;【乙】</note><sic n="0440012" corr="子" resp="【乙】">李</sic>形</note></lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>第二手執三五莖孔雀尾。從佛母
<lb n="0440a11"/>右邊右旋。周匝蓮華葉上。畫七佛世尊。從微
<lb n="0440a12"/>&CB00425;尸如來<note n="0440013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（次第布列）＋乃【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440013"><lem>乃</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">次第布列乃</rdg></app>至釋迦及慈氏菩薩等。皆<note n="0440014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">頭＝顧【聖】</note><app n="0440014"><lem>頭</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">顧</rdg></app>
<lb n="0440a13"/>向外坐各住定相。至西北角第八葉上。畫慈
<lb n="0440a14"/>氏菩薩。左手執軍持右手揚掌向外作<note n="0440015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔施〕－【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440015"><lem>施</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>無
<lb n="0440a15"/>畏勢。又於蓮華葉外。內院四方畫四辟支佛。
<lb n="0440a16"/>皆作佛形頂有肉髻亦住定相。<note n="0440016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔又於…從〕十字－【聖】</note><app n="0440016" word-count="10"><lem>又於四隅畫
<lb n="0440a17"/>四大聲聞。從</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>東北隅<note n="0440017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔畫〕－【聖】</note><app n="0440017"><lem>畫</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>阿難陀。次東南隅
<lb n="0440a18"/>畫羅&CB00264;羅。次西南隅畫舍利弗。次西北隅
<lb n="0440a19"/>畫大目<note n="0440018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">揵＝乾【明】【聖】【甲】＊</note><app n="0440018"><lem>揵</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">乾</rdg></app>連。皆著<anchor id="fxT19p0440a01"/>揵陀袈裟偏袒右臂。此
<lb n="0440a20"/>皆中院。次第二院畫八方天王并諸眷屬。東
<lb n="0440a21"/>方畫帝釋天王。執金剛杵與諸天眾圍遶。次
<lb n="0440a22"/>東南方畫火<note n="0440019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＋（王）【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440019"><lem>天</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">天王</rdg></app>。左手執軍持右手施無畏。與
<lb n="0440a23"/>五通苦行仙眾圍遶。次南方畫焰摩天王。執
<lb n="0440a24"/>焰摩幢。與焰摩<note n="0440020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔界〕－【乙】</note><app n="0440020"><lem>界</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0440021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔鬼〕－【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440021"><lem>鬼</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>眾圍遶次西南方畫
<lb n="0440a25"/>羅剎<note n="0440022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝主【明】【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440022"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">主</rdg></app>執刀。與諸羅剎眾圍遶。次西方畫
<lb n="0440a26"/>水<note n="0440023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＋（王）&M062403;【乙】</note><app n="0440023"><lem>天</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【乙】">天王</rdg></app>。持&CB00559;索。與諸龍眾圍遶。次西北方畫
<lb n="0440a27"/>風天王。執幢幡。與諸持明仙眾圍遶。次北
<lb n="0440a28"/>方畫多聞天王。執<note n="0440024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寶棒＝實持【聖】</note><app n="0440024"><lem>寶棒</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">實持</rdg></app>。與諸藥叉眾圍遶。
<lb n="0440a29"/>次東北方畫伊舍那天。執三戟叉。與諸步多
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0983A.0440b" n="0440b"/>
<lb n="0440b01"/>鬼眾圍遶。此皆<note n="0440025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是〕－【乙】</note><app n="0440025"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>第二院。次第三院從東
<lb n="0440b02"/>北隅。右旋周匝畫二十八大藥叉將。各與諸
<lb n="0440b03"/>鬼神眾圍遶。及畫宿曜十二宮神。次第三院
<lb n="0440b04"/>外周匝。用香泥塗<note n="0440026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飾＝拭【明】【甲】【乙】，滅【聖】</note><note n="0440026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飾＝拭【明】【甲】【乙】，＝滅【聖】</note><app n="0440026"><lem>飾</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">拭</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">滅</rdg></app>。布以荷葉。<note n="0440027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔葉〕－【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440027"><lem>葉</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>上<note n="0440028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔安〕－【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440028"><lem>安</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0440b05"/>置供養食<note n="0440029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＝器【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0440029"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">器</rdg></app>所謂乳<note n="0440030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">麋＝度【聖】</note><app n="0440030"><lem>麋</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">度</rdg></app>酪飯<note n="0440031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（飲）＋食【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0440031"><lem>食</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">飲食</rdg></app>果子等。皆
<lb n="0440b06"/>以阿波羅<note n="0440032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">爾＝&CB14031;【明】【乙】</note><app n="0440032"><lem>爾</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB14031;</rdg></app>多明王真言。加持香水散灑。布
<lb n="0440b07"/>列四邊供養。及以諸<note n="0440033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">漿＝將水【聖】</note><app n="0440033"><lem>漿</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">將水</rdg></app><note n="0440034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沙＝砂【明】【聖】【乙】</note><app n="0440034"><lem>沙</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【乙】" resp="Taisho">砂</rdg></app>糖石蜜石榴蜜
<lb n="0440b08"/>漿等而奉獻之。壇上散白色花於四角置<note n="0440035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">酥＝蘇【聖】【甲】＊</note><app n="0440035"><lem>酥</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">蘇</rdg></app>
<lb n="0440b09"/>燈四盞。四門各置二淨器滿盛香水。於壇東
<lb n="0440b10"/>安佛母大孔雀明王像。其畫像法如前畫壇。
<lb n="0440b11"/><note n="0440036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝准【聖】</note><app n="0440036"><lem>唯</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">准</rdg></app>不安界道即<note n="0440037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝界【聖】</note><app n="0440037"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">界</rdg></app>。中院聖眾燒沈香和<note n="0440038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔香〕－【甲】</note><app n="0440038"><lem>香</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0440b12"/>等供養。東方天眾應燒<note n="0440039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">白＝自【聖】</note><app n="0440039"><lem>白</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">自</rdg></app>膠香而為供養。南
<lb n="0440b13"/>方天眾以紫&CB00432;芥子<note n="0440040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔及〕－【聖】</note><app n="0440040"><lem>及</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>鹽相和燒之供養。西
<lb n="0440b14"/>方天眾以<anchor id="fxT19p0440b01"/>酥和安<note n="0440041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悉＝息【明】【乙】</note><app n="0440041"><lem>悉</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">息</rdg></app>香燒<note n="0440042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之供…眾〕七字－【聖】</note><app n="0440042" word-count="7"><lem>之供養。北方天
<lb n="0440b15"/>眾</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>應燒薰陸香而供養<note n="0440043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【甲】</note><app n="0440043"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。持<note n="0440044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦＝讀【聖】</note><app n="0440044"><lem>誦</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">讀</rdg></app>者於壇西
<lb n="0440b16"/><note n="0440045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔面〕－【明】【乙】</note><app n="0440045"><lem>面</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。敷茅薦為座。或坐<note n="0440046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">卑＝厘【明】，厚【聖】，庳【乙】</note><note n="0440046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">卑＝厘【明】，＝厚【聖】，＝庳【乙】</note><app n="0440046"><lem>卑</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">厘</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">厚</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">庳</rdg></app>&CB00560;床子。嚴飾經案
<lb n="0440b17"/>置於壇前。以諸香花供養經卷。應如是布列。
<lb n="0440b18"/>轉讀經者可三<note n="0440047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0440047"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>五人<note n="0440048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔乃至〕－【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440048"><lem>乃至</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>七人。更<note n="0440049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">替＝贊【聖】</note><app n="0440049"><lem>替</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">贊</rdg></app>相
<lb n="0440b19"/>續晝夜不令經聲間斷。<note n="0440050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔要在…場〕六十二字－【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440050" word-count="62"><lem>要在絕語言。除數內
<lb n="0440b20"/>一人明閑教法。&CB00057;師指撝取與<note n="0440051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祇＝祗【明】</note><app n="0440051"><lem>祇</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">祗</rdg></app>對。作法
<lb n="0440b21"/>結印啟請賢聖。餘人但當至心讀經。唯在遍
<lb n="0440b22"/>數多。慇重發願依三十七尊禮懺。三時或六
<lb n="0440b23"/>時。其道場</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>或一日或二日三日乃至七日。一
<lb n="0440b24"/>切災禍悉皆殄滅。除不至心。轉經者或在家
<lb n="0440b25"/>人或是出家人。每日澡浴清淨著新淨衣。<note n="0440052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">初＝禍【聖】</note><app n="0440052"><lem>初</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">禍</rdg></app>
<lb n="0440b26"/>起首時對道場前。虔誠一心禮諸聖眾。先以
<lb n="0440b27"/>印契真言。依教請召一切佛菩薩及諸<note n="0440053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＝大【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440053"><lem>天</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">大</rdg></app>眾。
<lb n="0440b28"/>如法供養。說所求事慇懃啟告。願垂加護。普
<lb n="0440b29"/>為一切苦難眾生。廣發大願。然後結跏趺坐
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0983A.0440c" n="0440c"/>
<lb n="0440c01"/>以塗香塗手。先結三昧耶印。二手<note n="0440054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔右〕－【聖】</note><app n="0440054"><lem>右</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>押左外
<lb n="0440c02"/>相叉作拳。直&CB00594;二中指頭相<note n="0440055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拄＝跓【聖】【甲】＊</note><app n="0440055"><lem>拄</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">跓</rdg></app>即成。結印當
<lb n="0440c03"/>心誦三昧耶真言七遍真言曰</p>
<lb n="0440c04"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0440056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唵＋（引一）細註【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0440056"><lem>唵</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>三<note n="0440057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＋（聲）【明】【乙】，〔去〕－【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440057"><lem><note place="inline">去</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">去聲</note></rdg><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0440058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">麼＝摩【聖】＊</note><app n="0440058"><lem>麼</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">摩</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0440059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＋（聲）【明】【乙】，（二）【聖】</note><app n="0440059"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">上聲</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">上二</rdg></app></note>野娑怛鍐<note place="inline"><note n="0440060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三合＝二合三【聖】</note><app n="0440060"><lem>三合</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">二合三</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0440c05"/><p>即以此印加持自身四處。所謂心額<note n="0440061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喉頂＝唯項【聖】</note><app n="0440061"><lem>喉頂</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">唯項</rdg></app>頂
<lb n="0440c06"/>上散印</p>
<lb n="0440c07"/><p>次結金剛鉤菩薩印</p>
<lb n="0440c08"/><p>准前三昧耶印。以二頭指屈如鉤向身<note n="0440062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">招＋（之）【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440062"><lem>招</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">招之</rdg></app>。不
<lb n="0440c09"/>間斷誦真言七遍。<note n="0440063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">普＝善【聖】</note><app n="0440063"><lem>普</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">善</rdg></app>召諸佛菩薩諸天鬼神
<lb n="0440c10"/>一切聖眾真言<note n="0440064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曰〕－【聖】</note><app n="0440064"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0440c11"/><p type="dharani"><anchor id="fxT19p0440c01"/>唵&CB00085;日<note n="0440065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03298;＝朗【明】【甲】【乙】，郎【聖】</note><note n="0440065" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB03298;＝朗【明】【甲】【乙】，＝郎【聖】</note><app n="0440065"><lem>&CB03298;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">朗</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">郎</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0440066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二合引＝引二合【聖】＊</note><app n="0440066"><lem>二合引</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">引二合</rdg></app></note>矩尸<note n="0440067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＝三【明】，二【乙】</note><note n="0440067" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一＝三【明】，＝二【乙】</note><app n="0440067"><lem><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">三</note></rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">二</note></rdg></app>阿<note place="inline">引</note>羯<note place="inline"><note n="0440068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">重＝序【聖】</note><app n="0440068"><lem>重</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">序</rdg></app>呼</note><note n="0440069" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">茶＝荼【明】【聖】【乙】＊，茶＋（三）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0440069"><lem>茶</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【乙】" resp="Taisho">荼</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">茶<note place="inline">三</note></rdg></app>微
<lb n="0440c12"/>羯<anchor id="fxT19p0440c02"/>茶娑&CB00085;<anchor id="fxT19p0440c03"/><note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0440070" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＋（引四）細註【明】【乙】，（引）細註【聖】，訶＝賀【聖】【甲】＊</note><app n="0440070"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">訶<note place="inline">引四</note></rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">訶<note place="inline">引</note></rdg><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">賀</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0440c13"/><p>由結此印誦真言請。召一切聖眾不違本誓
<lb n="0440c14"/>皆來赴<note n="0440071" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">集＋（會）【聖】，（其其會）【甲】</note><app n="0440071"><lem>集</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">集會</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">集其其會</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0440c15"/><p>次結阿波羅<anchor id="fxT19p0440c04"/>爾多明王印。用結地界結<note n="0440072" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">方＋（界結方）【甲】</note><app n="0440072"><lem>方</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">方界結方</rdg></app>
<lb n="0440c16"/>隅界。二手右押左內相叉。直&CB00594;<note n="0440073" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＝二【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0440073"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app>中指頭
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0983A.0441a" n="0441a"/>
<lb n="0441a01"/>相<anchor id="fxT19p0441a01"/>拄。<note n="0441001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＋（成）【聖】</note><app n="0441001"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">即成</rdg></app>以印頂上右旋三匝。隨心遠近便
<lb n="0441a02"/>成結界誦七遍真言曰</p>
<lb n="0441a03"/><p type="dharani"><anchor id="fxT19p0441a02"/>唵<note n="0441002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">虎＝護【聖】【甲】＊</note><app n="0441002"><lem>虎</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">護</rdg></app>嚕<anchor id="fxT19p0441a03"/>虎<note n="0441003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚕＋（二）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0441003"><lem>嚕</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">嚕<note place="inline">二</note></rdg></app>戰<note n="0441004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拏＋（引）夾註【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0441004"><lem>拏</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">拏<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app><note n="0441005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">里＋（三）細註【明】【乙】</note><app n="0441005"><lem>里</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">里<note place="inline">三</note></rdg></app><note n="0441006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＋（引）細註【甲】</note><app n="0441006"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">摩<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>蹬岐<note place="inline"><note n="0441007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＋（聲四）【明】【聖】【乙】，（夷反去）【甲】</note><app n="0441007"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【乙】" resp="Taisho">去聲四</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">去夷反去</rdg></app></note>娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0441a04"/><note place="inline">二合引</note><anchor id="fxT19p0441a04"/>訶<note place="inline"><note n="0441008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（五）【明】【乙】</note><app n="0441008"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">引五</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0441a05"/><p>次結普供養一切<note n="0441009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賢聖＝聖眾【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0441009"><lem>賢聖</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">聖眾</rdg></app>印</p>
<lb n="0441a06"/><p>二手右押左相叉合掌。十指互交上節即成。
<lb n="0441a07"/>結印當心<note n="0441010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦＋（真言）【甲】</note><app n="0441010"><lem>誦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">誦真言</rdg></app>七遍頂上散印真言曰</p>
<lb n="0441a08"/><p type="dharani">曩莫三滿多<note n="0441011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">勃＝母【甲】</note><app n="0441011"><lem>勃</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">母</rdg></app>馱<note n="0441012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【明】【聖】【乙】</note><app n="0441012"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>南<note place="inline">一</note>薩&CB00085;佗<note place="inline">引二</note>欠<note place="inline"><note n="0441013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">平＋（聲）【明】【乙】，平＝三【甲】</note><app n="0441013"><lem>平</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">平聲</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">三</rdg></app>三</note>
<lb n="0441a09"/>嗢娜<note n="0441014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00754;＝&CB00752;【明】【乙】</note><app n="0441014"><lem>&CB00754;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00752;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">四</note>娑<note n="0441015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03568;＝頗【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0441015"><lem>&CB03568;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">頗</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>囉呬<note place="inline">馨異<note n="0441016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝切【明】【乙】</note><app n="0441016"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">切</rdg></app>引</note>&CB00805;<note place="inline">五</note>&CB00344;
<lb n="0441a10"/>&CB00344;曩劍<note n="0441017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔六〕－【甲】</note><app n="0441017"><lem><note place="inline">六</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0441018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＋（引七）細註【明】【乙】，訶＝賀【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0441018"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">訶<note place="inline">引七</note></rdg><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">賀</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0441a11"/><p>由結此印及誦真言。能於一一佛菩薩諸聖
<lb n="0441a12"/>眾前及於無量諸佛剎土。<note n="0441019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自成辦至養八字聖本作夾註</note><note n="0441019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（成辦一切廣大供養）八字本文＝（成辦一切廣大供養）八字夾註【聖】</note><app n="0441019"><lem>成辦一切廣大供
<lb n="0441a13"/>養</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">成辦一切廣大供養</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0441a14"/><p>次結佛母大孔雀明王印</p>
<lb n="0441a15"/><p>二手右押左內相叉。二大指二小指。各直&CB00594;
<lb n="0441a16"/>頭相<anchor id="fxT19p0441a05"/>拄即成。結<note n="0441020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔印〕－【聖】</note><app n="0441020"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>當心誦真言七遍。如<note n="0441021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">前＝上【明】【乙】</note><app n="0441021"><lem>前</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">上</rdg></app>
<lb n="0441a17"/>以印加持四<note n="0441022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">處＝虔【明】</note><app n="0441022"><lem>處</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">虔</rdg></app>頂上散印真言曰</p>
<lb n="0441a18"/><p type="dharani"><anchor id="fxT19p0441a06"/>唵<anchor id="fxT19p0441a07"/>麼庾<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0441023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0441023"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note><note n="0441024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訖＝說【聖】</note><app n="0441024"><lem>訖</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">說</rdg></app>蘭<note place="inline">二合<note n="0441025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【聖】【甲】＊</note><app n="0441025"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>帝<note n="0441026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【明】【甲】</note><app n="0441026"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT19p0441a08"/>引</note>
<lb n="0441a19"/><note n="0441027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＝訶引二【明】【乙】，賀引【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0441027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶＝訶引二【明】【乙】，＝賀引【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0441027"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">訶引二</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">賀引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0441a20"/><p>次捧香爐奉獻啟請。告<note n="0441028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔白〕－【明】【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0441028"><lem>白</lem><rdg wit="【明】【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>聖眾說所求事。如
<lb n="0441a21"/>是依法請召供養已。然後起悲愍心。為拔濟
<lb n="0441a22"/>眾生苦難故。轉讀此經。每日中前換<note n="0441029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸供＝供養【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0441029"><lem>諸供</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">供養</rdg></app>
<lb n="0441a23"/>物。應結阿<note n="0441030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">波＝婆【聖】</note><app n="0441030"><lem>波</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app>羅<anchor id="fxT19p0441a09"/>爾多明王印誦本真言。以
<lb n="0441a24"/>印頂上左旋一匝。暫解其界換供養已。即如
<lb n="0441a25"/>前次第再迎請結界如是依教供養轉讀此
<lb n="0441a26"/>經。所有災難<note n="0441031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">亢＝&CB00057;【聖】</note><app n="0441031"><lem>亢</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&CB00057;</rdg></app>旱疾疫。鬼魅厭禱惡毒災
<lb n="0441a27"/>障。種種苦難必得除滅。所有祈願無不遂心。
<lb n="0441a28"/>我<note n="0441032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＋（今）【聖】</note><app n="0441032"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">已今</rdg></app>廣說畫像壇場供養儀軌竟。若不<note n="0441033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">辦＝辯【明】，辨【甲】</note><note n="0441033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">辦＝辯【明】，＝辨【甲】</note><app n="0441033"><lem>辦</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">辯</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">辨</rdg></app>
<lb n="0441a29"/>如是塗畫壇場。或有急速災難<note n="0441034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">至＋（時）【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0441034"><lem>至</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">至時</rdg></app>。可隨自
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0983A.0441b" n="0441b"/>
<lb n="0441b01"/>力分於一淨處。以瞿摩夷塗地作一<note n="0441035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔肘〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0441035"><lem>肘</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>方壇。
<lb n="0441b02"/><note n="0441036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">隨＋（意）【聖】【乙】</note><app n="0441036"><lem>隨</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【乙】" resp="Taisho">隨意</rdg></app><note n="0441037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其＝畢【甲】</note><app n="0441037"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">畢</rdg></app>大小。<note n="0441038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">磨＝麼【聖】</note><app n="0441038"><lem>磨</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>白檀香塗作圓壇。九位中安
<lb n="0441b03"/>佛像。及以三五莖孔雀尾<note n="0441039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00594;＝賢【聖】</note><app n="0441039"><lem>&CB00594;</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">賢</rdg></app>於壇<note n="0441040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（中）＋上【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0441040"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">中上</rdg></app>。隨時
<lb n="0441b04"/>燒香散花乳<note n="0441041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">糜＝摩【聖】</note><app n="0441041"><lem>糜</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">摩</rdg></app>酪<note n="0441042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">等＝飲【聖】，&CB10166;【甲】</note><note n="0441042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">等＝飲【聖】，＝&CB10166;【甲】</note><app n="0441042"><lem>等</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">飲</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB10166;</rdg></app>供養聖眾。但虔誠一
<lb n="0441b05"/>心轉讀此經。<note n="0441043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔或一遍〕－【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0441043"><lem>或一遍</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>或三遍乃至七遍。或一
<lb n="0441b06"/>日或二日。一切厄難悉得消除。所有祈願皆
<lb n="0441b07"/>得圓滿</p>
<lb n="0441b08"/><p>爾時阿難陀聞佛世尊。為當來<note n="0441044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔世〕－【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0441044"><lem>世</lem><rdg wit="【聖】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>一切苦難
<lb n="0441b09"/>有情。說此讀誦大孔雀明王經法。頂戴受持
<lb n="0441b10"/>禮佛而退</p>
<lb n="0441b11"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><note n="0441045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0441045"><lem>佛<anchor id="fxT19p0441b01"/>說</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>大孔雀明王<note n="0441046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔畫像壇場〕－【甲】</note><app n="0441046"><lem>畫像壇場</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>儀軌<note n="0441047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（法一）＋卷【聖】，（一）＋卷【甲】，〔卷〕－【乙】，乙本奧書曰貞享三年仲秋十一夜訓點了河南教興傳密沙門淨嚴四十有八元祿十六年正月二十五日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊教</note><app n="0441047"><lem><note place="inline">卷</note></lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">法一卷</note></rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">一卷</note></rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0441047" place="foot" type="rest">乙本奧書曰貞享三年仲秋十一夜訓點了河南教興傳密沙門淨嚴四十有八元祿十六年正月二十五日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊教</note></jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
